[IMAGE]
Three images showing different perspectives of the property:
1. Side view of the building with a narrow alleyway and adjacent residential buildings.
1. Rear view showing a parking area with several cars.
1. Close-up of the building's utility meters mounted on the exterior wall.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image showing a stairwell with a brick wall and mailboxes on the right side. The stairwell has a carpeted floor and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a door at the end of a hallway with a painting on the left wall. The hallway has a carpeted floor and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a brick apartment building exterior with a red awning over the entrance. The building has multiple windows with air conditioning units.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with a painting on the wall and carpeted steps. The stairwell has metal railings.
[/IMAGE]
